color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=6111362b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"ab2157d1c34741849b47fb407319e1d82f0757d7","tid":2032874,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ddffc7b822472e5b2f25f97283b66039938987b","tid":2032874,"uid":136661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b699bbfee155415b7eb9e6f9761fa13b9365c37d","tid":2032874,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c2000bff0ab7752983e0924f4a1439997393f1e8","tid":2032874,"uid":53258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:23:12.000Z","msg":"白警嚟架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\"